seo: Spring Actuator,信息泄露,漏洞检测,安全扫描
seo_en: Spring Actuator, information leakage, vulnerability detection, security scanning
summary: 该插件用于检测Spring Actuator接口的信息泄露漏洞，通过遍历目录和扫描特定节点来发现未授权访问的问题。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect information leakage vulnerabilities in Spring Actuator interfaces by traversing directories and scanning specific nodes to identify unauthorized access issues.
